                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18010114-108-off609 t18010114-108-cd610"></join>, a coat, value 5s. two waistcoats, value 5s. a shirt, value 2s. a stock, value 6d. and a silver stock buckle, value 5s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18010114-108-victim1016" type="victimName">
                     John 
                     Hampson
                  <interp inst="t18010114-108-victim1016" type="surname" value="Hampson"></interp>
